ualification with 14.966 points.\", \"from\": 905, \"to\": 1064, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 941, \"end\": 945, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Yulo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.7096574730947972e-43, \"text\": \"Yulo\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Yulo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Yulo\"}, {\"begin\": 987, \"end\": 1000, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_women's_national_field_hockey_team\", \"score\": 0.9900863798417051, \"rank\": 0.009547764739442242, \"text\": \"Great Britain\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_women's_national_field_hockey_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_women's_national_field_hockey_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1003, \"end\": 1007, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Animorphs\", \"score\": 0.9774189084736403, \"rank\": 0.010871541604833192, \"text\": \"Jake\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Animorphs\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Animorphs\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Jarman, who's born to a Filipina mother, has shown consistency in the apparatus in this Olympics as he also netted the highest floor exercise score in theall-around final, where he posted 14.900 points.\", \"from\": 1066, \"to\": 1268, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1090, \"end\": 1098, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Filipinos\", \"score\": 0.9814331378073666, \"rank\": 0.018918112145402535, \"text\": \"Filipina\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Filipinos\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Filipinos\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Like Yulo, Jarman is seeking his first Olympic medal.\", \"from\": 1270, \"to\": 1323, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Reigning Olympic champion Artem Dolgopyat of Israel also advanced to the final, although he placed a distant seventh in the qualification with 14.466 poi